summary: This is my saved game that I finished a few days ago. By finished, I mean reaching lvl 81 without cheats, beating the main storyline, and that of Dawnguard and Dragonborn. Hope you like it.
descriptionHtml:
Name: Malgus

Level: 81

Race: Nord

Civil War: Stormcloaks

Main storyline beaten, as well as Dawnguard (Vampires), and Dragonborn. Not all quests have been completed. I'm uploading this file for the sole purpose of keeping a backup of it on the Nexus because my PC has a bad "habit" of accumulating viruses, there requiring me to do a system restore, destroying the save in the process. Finished all of the guilds storylines in Skyrim.
author: Malgus37
